  "body": "Here is the code.\r\n```\r\n<template>\r\n  <scroller class=\"scroll\"\r\n            scrollDirection=\"horizontal\"\r\n            :style=\"{height: layoutHeight}\">\r\n    <slot\r\n      v-for=\"item in items\"\r\n      :item=\"item\"\r\n      :width=\"layoutWidth\"\r\n      :height=\"layoutHeight - 2*layoutMargin\"\r\n      :margin=\"layoutMargin\">\r\n    </slot>\r\n    <loading style=\"width:200; height: 200;flex-direction: row;justify-content: center;\" :display=\"show\">\r\n      <loading-indicator style=\"height:160;width:160;color:#3192e1\"></loading-indicator>\r\n    </loading>\r\n  </scroller>\r\n</template>\r\n<style scoped>\r\n  .scroll {\r\n    background-color: #f5f5f5;\r\n    flex-direction: row;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut, when scrollDirection is vertical, loading view works!",
